## clock-frequency

Property: `clock-frequency`

Value type: `<prop-encoded-array>`

Specifies the frequency of a clock in Hz. The value is a `<prop-encoded-array>` in one of two forms:

a 32-bit integer consisting of one `<u32>` specifying the frequency.

a 64-bit integer represented as a `<u64>` specifying the frequency.'s input clock.

```dts
/* arch/arm/boot/dts/aspeed-g5.dtsi */
clk_clkin: clk_clkin {
    compatible = "fixed-clock";
    #clock-cells = <0>;
    clock-frequency = <25000000>;
};

/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/fsl/mpc8572ds.dts */
cpu@0 {
    clock-frequency = <825000000>;
};
```

---

**From binding** (\`qcom,sm8550-cci\`):

Frequency of the main oscillator.
